metadata.description:
Photography | Ai | Photoshop
6000 x 6000

Colors of Love is a limited series of 1 of 1 mixed media artworks by accomplished Australian artist and provocateur AprilYFU. Lovingly crafting works that are beautiful, often disarming, and sometimes confronting, with a focus on the sensuality of the female form, sex, love, alternate dimensions and worlds.
